   {
      "body" : "If there is no valid reason to keep it (or set the default to true) bitcoin-core should not encourage bad practice (Not to mention the documentation inconsistencies: Both, `paytxfee` and `settxfee` are in BTC/kB). The earlier we get rid of that, the better.\r\n\r\nIntroducing a CLI/RPC parameter is trivial but serves no purpose, if there is no compelling reason to do so. We could still leave the flag in the source code for some grace period to let people modify it by hand if they really need it?",
      "created_at" : "2015-09-28T12:39:15Z",
