      "body" : "This will produce the smallest diff but if it is preferred to make `check_fee_amount()` independent of `curr_balance`. I.e. `def check_fee_amount(self, actual_fee, fee_per_byte, tx_size):`, it could later also be used by other classes in the framework.",
